'''北撲翅鴷'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Colaptes auratus''）是[[撲翅鴷屬|撲翅鴷屬]]下的一種中型啄木鳥，分佈于[[北美洲|北美洲]]大部和[[中美洲|中美洲]]部分地區、[[古巴|古巴]]及[[開曼群島|開曼群島]]。這是一種在分佈地區常見的鳥類，其俗稱有上百種。

==分類==

[[File:Northern_Flicker_on_Seedskadee_National_Wildlife_Refuge_(25906541634).jpg|thumb]]]]其下有十個亞種<ref name=ITIS>{{cite web|url= https://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/SingleRpt?search_topic=TSN&search_value=178154|title= Colaptes auratus report|website= ITIS Report|publisher= Integrated Taxonomic Information System|access-date= 27 March 2016|archive-date= 2020-08-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200805080422/https://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/SingleRpt?search_topic=TSN&search_value=178154|dead-url= no}}</ref>。[[指名亞種|指名亞種]]''Colaptes auratus auratus''（英語稱“yellow-shafted flicker”）分佈於北美東部，這一種即是[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]的[[美國州鳥列表|州鳥]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.archives.state.al.us/emblems/st_bird.html |title=Alabama State Bird |accessdate=2007-03-18 |date=2006-04-27 |work=Alabama Emblems, Symbols and Honors |publisher=Alabama Department of Archives & History |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224225424/http://www.archives.state.al.us/emblems/st_bird.html%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 此外還有生活在北美洲西部的''Colaptes auratus cafer''（英語稱“red-shafted flicker”）等。''Colaptes auratus/cafer rufipileus''在1910年代滅絕。

==描述==
{{listen|filename=Colaptes auratus.ogg|title=Northern flicker|description=1996年8月[[長島|長島]]一隻北撲翅鴷的叫聲}}
兩性成年北撲翅鴷羽毛為褐色，有深黑色條紋，體長在{{convert|28|-|36|cm|in}}之間，翼展在{{convert|42|-|54|cm|in}}之間。體重則在{{convert|86|to|167|g|oz}}之間。<ref name = "CRC">''CRC Handbook of Avian Body Masses'' by John B. Dunning Jr. (Editor). CRC Press (1992), ISBN 978-0-8493-4258-5.</ref> 翼骨長度為{{convert|12.2|-|17.1|cm|in}}，尾巴長度為{{convert|7.5|-|11.5|cm|in}}，喙長{{convert|2.2|-|4.3|cm|in}}，蹠骨長{{convert|2.2|-|3.1|cm|in}}。雄性的北撲翅鴷的[[鳥喙|鳥喙]]根部有紅色或黑色的[[髭|髭]]。生活在北方地區的北撲翅鴷體型較大，[[大開曼|大開曼]]的北撲翅鴷體型最小。<ref>''Woodpeckers: An Identification Guide to the Woodpeckers of the World'' by Hans Winkler, David A. Christie & David Nurney. Houghton Mifflin (1995), ISBN 978-0-395-72043-1</ref>

==習性==
[[奥杜邦学会|奥杜邦学会]]稱，這是唯一經常在地面尋找食物的啄木鳥。它們有時也會捕捉飛行中的昆蟲。其主食為各類昆蟲，但也吃植物漿果和種子（尤其是冬天）。它們的食譜中，45%為螞蟻。它們會啄木穿地面，捕捉藏在巢穴中的食物。它們的舌頭能探出{{Convert|50|mm|in|abbr=on}}長。它是入侵北美的農業害蟲[[玉米螟|玉米螟]]的天敵。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.ent.iastate.edu/pest/cornborer/insect|title=The European Corn Borer {{!}} The European Corn Borer|website=www.ent.iastate.edu|access-date=2017-11-13|archive-date=2017-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170611045247/http://www.ent.iastate.edu/pest/cornborer/insect|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://entnemdept.ufl.edu/creatures/field/e_corn_borer.htm|title=European corn borer - Ostrinia nubilalis (Hubner)|website=entnemdept.ufl.edu|access-date=2017-11-13|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530041733/http://entnemdept.ufl.edu/creatures/field/e_corn_borer.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==生命週期==
它們一般最多活六年左右，只有0.6%的北撲翅鴷能活到第七年<ref name="Fisher2006">{{cite journal |last1=Fisher |first1=Ryan J. |last2=Wiebe |first2=Karen L. |title=Effects of Sex and Age on Survival of Northern Flickers: A Six-Year Field Study. |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_condor_2006-02_108_1/page/193 |journal=The Condor |date=2006 |volume=108 |issue=1 |pages=193–200 |jstor=4123207 |doi=10.1650/0010-5422(2006)108[0193:EOSAAO]2.0.CO;2 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Fisher |first1=Ryan J. |last2=Wiebe |first2=Karen L. |title=Effects of Sex and Age on Survival of Northern Flickers: A Six-Year Field Study. |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_condor_2006-02_108_1/page/193 |journal=The Condor |date=2006 |volume=108 |issue=1 |pages=193–200 |jstor=4123207 |doi=10.1650/0010-5422(2006)108[0193:EOSAAO]2.0.CO;2 }}</ref>，雌雄之間沒有太大差異。其壽命最高紀錄為9年零2個月。<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=http://www.allaboutbirds.org/guide/Northern_Flicker/lifehistory |title=Northern Flicker |accessdate=2015-10-03 |publisher=The Cornell Lab of Ornithology (All About Birds) |archive-date=2015-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006013228/http://www.allaboutbirds.org/guide/Northern_Flicker/lifehistory |dead-url=no }}</ref>

